Are marriages performed outside the U.S. recognized by the U.S.? Maybe gays and lesbians should be allowed to marry in Canada. And if they stay there for their honey moon, they would have killed two birds with one stone. Then, when they come back, they would have bypassed all the crap.God! This is getting complicated. Forget I said anything.